{"parse":{"title":"First Campaign against Turkomen Hazaras","pageid":38274555,"revid":818646407,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-stack mobile-float-reset\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;float:right;clear:right\"><div style=\"overflow:hidden;margin:1px\"><table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"summary\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">First Campaign against Turkmen Hazaras</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><table style=\"width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0\"><tbody><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Date</th><td>December 28, 1505 \u2013 January, 1506 C.E.</td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Location</th><td><span class=\"location\">Northern <a href=\"/wiki/Hazarajat\" title=\"Hazarajat\">Hazarajat</a> near western extremities of <a href=\"/wiki/Hindu_Kush\" title=\"Hindu Kush\">Hindu Kush</a> mountains near the banks of Baran River, <a href=\"/wiki/Afghanistan\" title=\"Afghanistan\">Afghanistan</a></span></td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Result</th><td>\nSuccessful operations against the Hazaras.</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Belligerents</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Timurids\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Timurids\">Timurids</a> of <a href=\"/wiki/Kabul\" title=\"Kabul\">Kabul</a></td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Hazaras\" title=\"Hazaras\">Turkmen Hazaras</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Commanders and leaders</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Babur\" title=\"Babur\">Zahir-ud-din Muhammad Babur</a><br />Qasim Beg<br />Sheikh Dervish <i>Kokaltash</i> &#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Killed_in_action\" title=\"Killed in action\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;Old English Text MT&#39;,serif\"><b>&#8224;</b></span></a><br />Muhammad Ali Mubashar Beg &#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Killed_in_action\" title=\"Killed in action\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;Old English Text MT&#39;,serif\"><b>&#8224;</b></span></a><br /> Kup\u016bk Kuli Baba<br />Sultan Kuli Chan\u0101k <br />Khatim <i>Qurbegi</i><br />Y\u0101rek Tagh\u0101i<br />Ahmed Y\u016bsuf Beg</td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\n?</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div style=\"overflow:hidden;margin:1px\"><div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Campaigns_of_Babur\" style=\"margin:0;float:right;clear:right;width:25.5em;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-left:1em;;padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Campaignbox_Babur\" title=\"Template:Campaignbox Babur\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Campaignbox_Babur\" title=\"Template talk:Campaignbox Babur\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Babur&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id=\"Campaigns_of_Babur\" style=\"font-size:114%;margin:0 4em\"><span style=\"line-height:1.6em\">Campaigns of <a href=\"/wiki/Babur\" title=\"Babur\">Babur</a></span></div></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Siege_of_Samarkand_(1494)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Siege of Samarkand (1494)\">1st Samarkand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Siege_of_Samarkand_(1497)\" title=\"Siege of Samarkand (1497)\">2nd Samarkand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Siege_of_Samarkand_(1501)\" title=\"Siege of Samarkand (1501)\">3rd Samarkand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Battle_of_Sar-e-Pul\" title=\"Battle of Sar-e-Pul\">Sar-e-Pul</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Uzbek_Conquest_of_Samarkand_(1501)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Uzbek Conquest of Samarkand (1501) (page does not exist)\">4th Samarkand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Battle_of_Akhsi\" title=\"Battle of Akhsi\">Akhsi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Siege_of_Kabul_(1504)\" title=\"Siege of Kabul (1504)\">Kabul</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Campaign_against_Sultan_Masudi_Hazaras\" title=\"Campaign against Sultan Masudi Hazaras\">Masudi Hazaras</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Babur%27s_First_Indian_Expedition\" title=\"Babur&#39;s First Indian Expedition\">1st India</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Battle_of_Qalat\" title=\"Battle of Qalat\">Qalat-e Ghilji</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">1st Turkomen Hazaras</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Second_Campaign_against_Turkomen_Hazaras&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Second Campaign against Turkomen Hazaras (page does not exist)\">2nd Turkomen Hazaras</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Babur%27s_Campaign_against_Ghilji_Afghans&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" cla